data.name: Sample - Google Key Management Service - 1.0.0
data.description: Sample playbooks for "Google Key Management Service" connector. If you are planning to use any of the sample playbooks in your environment, ensure that you clone those playbooks and move them to a different collection, since the sample playbook collection gets deleted during connector upgrade and delete.
